headline: Despite his $2.6 billion net worth, MrBeast says he’s having to borrow cash and doesn’t even have enough money in his bank account to buy McDonald’s
summary: Jimmy Donaldson, the world’s most popular YouTuber and founder of $5 billion business Beast Industries, claims he doesn’t “technically” have enough money to buy McDonald’s in the morning.

headline: McDonald's (MCD): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Since July 2025, McDonald's has been in a holding pattern, posting a small return of 1.5% while floating around $306.50. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 11.1% gain during that period.
